I am an Honorary Research Associate at [Imperial College London](https://www.imperial.ac.uk/).

I run [Ifestos.ai](https://ifestos.ai), a robotics research consulting agency.

Before that I was a Senior Research Science Manager at Meta Reality Labs Research, Head of Research at [Scape Technologies](https://techcrunch.com/2020/02/08/scapebook/), and a post-doctoral researcher at the [University of Oxford](https://www.ox.ac.uk/).

Area chair and multiple outstanding reviewer awards at CVPR, ICCV, and other computer vision conferences. Young Researcher Travel Award at CVPR 2017. BAE and Thales MSc awards, 2009.
